content.title: RHBA-2018:0489: Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform 3.9 RPM Release Advisory (Moderate)
content.description:
Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform is the company's cloud computing
Platform-as-a-Service (PaaS) solution designed for on-premise or private cloud deployments.

The OpenShift Container Platform 3.9 Release Notes provide information about new features, bug fixes, and known issues:

https://docs.openshift.com/container-platform/3.9/release_notes/ocp_3_9_release_notes.html

This advisory contains the RPM packages for this release. See the following
advisory for the container images for this release:

https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHBA-2018:0490
